            <div class="r-container">
                <div class="row row-cols-lg-1 row-cols-1">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-xs-12 col-md-8 pe-lg-5  order-second">
                        <div class="info-para">
                            <div class="header-block">
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Comprehensive Geriatric Assessments: </strong>Conducting thorough evaluations to assess the overall health, functional status, and cognitive abilities of older adults.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Personalized Longevity Plans: </strong>Developing individualized care plans that incorporate preventive measures, lifestyle modifications, and treatments to promote healthy aging and longevity.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Chronic Disease Management: </strong>Providing specialized care for managing chronic conditions commonly seen in older adults, such as diabetes, hypertension, and osteoarthritis.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Functional Medicine Evaluations: </strong>Using a holistic approach to assess and address underlying imbalances that may contribute to age-related health issues.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Regenerative Therapies: </strong>Offering innovative treatments, such as stem cell therapy or platelet-rich plasma (PRP) therapy, to support tissue repair and regeneration.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Hormone Replacement Therapy: </strong>Providing hormone replacement options to address hormonal imbalances that can affect aging and overall health.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Nutritional Counseling and Supplements: </strong>Offering guidance on optimal nutrition, dietary supplements, and nutraceuticals to support healthy aging and longevity.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Physical Rehabilitation Services: </strong>Providing specialized rehabilitation programs to improve mobility, strength, and functional independence in older adults.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Cognitive Health Programs: </strong>Offering assessments, therapies, and cognitive training programs to support brain health and cognitive function in aging individuals.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Palliative Care and End-of-Life Planning: </strong>Providing compassionate care for individuals with advanced illnesses and offering support for end-of-life planning and decision-making.
                                </p>
                                 <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Genomic Medicine Services: </strong>Utilizing genetic testing and personalized medicine approaches to tailor treatment plans based on an individual's genetic profile and risk factors.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Health Promotion and Wellness Programs: </strong>Offering educational workshops, exercise classes, and wellness initiatives to promote healthy lifestyle habits and preventive care.
                                </p>
